{"tid":2201074,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家最唔鍾意邊個交友app？","createTime":"2020-09-13T13:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T16:17:55.000Z","uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"361212e907dd06681addfb11cf809c2d065f85fc","tid":2201074,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:22:37.000Z","msg":"app設計邏輯有問題<br />\n<br />\n或者裡面player太多 好難搵真心<br />\n<br />\n最討厭同最鍾意係邊隻"},{"pid":"18ee4fcbcf1141508339c1e6dbc1a15313b5d5c7","tid":2201074,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:25:20.000Z","msg":"Hmd sp app"},{"pid":"165bb327ed20c8078bab6bc4198828f26906038f","tid":2201074,"uid":123308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:25:22.000Z","msg":"補充資料：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">Omi -&gt; 「Tantan Hong Kong」-&gt; 背後公司：大陸 Tantan 探探</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然面頭嗰浸係改咗名做「MatchUp UK」取代「Tantan Hong Kong」"},{"pid":"01e731a80da261dff3a803b53fe0b6422f67b280","tid":2201074,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"（2018 年尾聖誕版本）各大交友平台 / 交友 apps 上綫啦！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/948957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/948957</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>又到聖誕旅遊旺季 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同時亦都係出 pool 旺季 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未有另一半？咁係時候要睇吓今個 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網上有相關 post 但都有一段歷史冇 update，修改下後畀大家參考，集思廣益 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><ins><span class=\"x-large\">交友平台</span></ins></span>，由舊到新排列：<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">緣份配對計劃- Match Up</span><br />\n以 Excel 形式打 'CV' 嘅交友平台始祖，不過已摺埋<br />\n個網雖然寫住「開發人員正在更新全新計劃!」，但唔見有甚何跡象個網會復活<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">www.hkg-match.ga</span><br />\n已摺埋<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">Skylight</span><br />\n已摺埋，當時僅限香港 UGC 八大 + SYU + OUHK 大學生參加<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">緣份相遇計劃- Triangel</span><br />\n已摺埋，「最新」嘅 post 都已經係舊年 2017 年年尾：<br />\n<ins>!!!緣份相遇計劃 Triangel &ndash; 最終回 !!! 10月1日(Sun) 報名開放</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/414102/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/414102/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n以上四個平台主要玩法係用文字打 CV，幾日時間畀你睇人哋 CV 揀人，match 中就交換 contact，但當然唔包生仔<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"x-large\">相關交友平台：</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">「新緣份配對計劃」Nextravel</span><br />\n好可惜，又係去到舊年 2017 年年尾就摺埋，最新嘅 post：<br />\n<ins>新緣份配對計劃 - 聖誕特別企劃</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/466615/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/466615/page/1</a><br />\n玩法應該係撞三個號碼，睇下人地揀唔揀中你 set 個 number，中就交換 contact<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">HeyMandi</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNBVu4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNBVu4w.jpg&h=ecce0273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事隔一年，至今 2018 年年尾仍然運行中，呢度有相關巴打開嘅 post：<br />\n<ins>[𢯎水吹] 與陌生展開超激情對話(3) - An撞都有App</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/472512/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/472512/page/1</a><br />\n玩法大致上係冇相冇資料，每個人只有 nickname，以話題為主，<br />\n詳情入去巴打個 post 睇<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">HowsYourDate</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqWBZfq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqWBZfq.jpg&h=aa2aecca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日隨機抽獎，冇樣睇，冇 voice message，當抽獎識朋友<br />\n詳情睇相關巴打開嘅 post：<br />\n<ins>[傾計App] HowsYourDate [有得Send 相啦] [7]</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/946494/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/946494/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n輪到<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\"><ins>交友 apps：</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n=====<ins>Made in Hong Kong:</ins>=====<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">MaskOFF</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4S9WYUv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4S9WYUv.jpg&h=9c7ad156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n背後公司係 Richard Li 嘅 Stakk，但間公司已經唔存在，個 app 亦因此摺埋<br />\n個 app 玩法幾創新，冇相，但可以打個人簡介，用聲音同對方傾計，<br />\n然後入下一階段打電話，再入 AR animoji 咁樣 FaceTime，最後真 face-to-face FaceTime<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">My Cup of Tea</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MsjDsRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMsjDsRF.jpg&h=ae1f513d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本地土炮，個 pool 唔太大，無大多相關用後報告，歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">2Date</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VhhtP6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhhtP6c.jpg&h=04799e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同樣係本地土炮，個 pool 似乎亦唔大，加上高登巴打評語麻麻，自己衡量<br />\n<ins>2DATE值得我課金嗎？<br />\n</ins><a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6765267&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6765267%26page%3D1&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8HwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=b2fce0a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6765267&amp;page=1</a><br />\n由上面個 post 可見，似乎有大量 bot，迫人課金，fake girls<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">ECFriend</span><br />\n本地土炮，但個 app 十世冇 update，iPhone iOS 11 打後用唔到 (32-bit)，<br />\n可想而知背後有冇動力去做，<br />\n無大多相關用後報告，歡迎各巴打補充<br />\n<br />\n=====<ins>Made in USA:</ins>=====<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">Tinder</span> (from USA company IAC，IAC 旗下有 Expedia、Trivago 等等)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvPv3tS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvPv3tS.jpg&h=9b60fd12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔需要多介紹，睇 iOS App Store 有 4.78K comments，<br />\n再睇 Google Play Store 個一億下載次數就知全世界最多人用，香港都唔例外<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">OkCupid</span> (also from USA company IAC)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UO7EWQc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUO7EWQc.jpg&h=cbc050cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩之前要填一啲關於你嘅個人喜好，再可以答埋一啲問題然後先玩<br />\n你所填嘅個人喜好同埋問題答案（例如宗教對你嚟講重唔重要？Yes or No?），<br />\n會用嚟畀系統對比你所填嘅答案，計到你同你個男仔／女仔究竟幾多 % 相似<br />\nOkCupid 本來唔需要 match 咗先可以講嘢，但 2017 年年尾改咗玩法，<br />\n都係要 match 咗先可以講嘢：<br />\n<a href=\"https://theblog.okcupid.com/why-okcupid-is-changing-how-you-message-f14d492e7853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheblog.okcupid.com%2Fwhy-okcupid-is-changing-how-you-message-f14d492e7853&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8HwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=559c0544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theblog.okcupid.com/why-okcupid-is-changing-how-you-message-f14d492e7853</a><br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">Happn</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPOHUCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPOHUCQ.jpg&h=47b407bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩法同上面啲 apps 有啲唔同，就係 app 入面你見到嘅人，就係你現實生活同你擦身而過嘅人，用 GPS 計算。個 pool 多唔多人視乎你每日返工／返學路徑，或者多唔多去一啲人多嘅地方，而人哋亦有用呢個 app<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">Coffee Meets Bagel</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GavjgP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GavjgP.jpg&h=034e4a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同 OkCupid 差唔多，根據你所填嘅資料同偏好設定，每日建議一啲人畀你 (suggested)，<br />\n同時亦可以主動搵符合你搜尋選項嘅人 (discover)，<br />\n不過不論係 suggested 定係 discover，每日都有人數限制，貴精不貴多<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">Skout</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wkq3D5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkq3D5e.jpg&h=9bd9dc66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個都應該唔需要多介紹，出名多狗公，龍蛇混雜，約炮私鐘為主<br />\n見到啱嘅人就可以講嘢，唔需要 match<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">Badoo</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAqrBS1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAqrBS1.jpg&h=6b3aa3b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">Hot or Not</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhbisZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhbisZM.jpg&h=7a92d309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擺佢哋喺一齊係因為其實表面上係兩個 apps，但背後其實係同一個 database，<br />\n基本上用是但一個就等於用埋另一個。<br />\n香港唔太常用，多 MK 妹，賓賓都唔少<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\"><a href=\"http://Match.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMatch.com&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8HwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=5f438d4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Match.com</a></span> (from USA company IAC)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRReLMX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRReLMX.jpg&h=d86b4ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1995 年就開站，香港都有個官方網站，但其實香港冇乜人用<br />\n<br />\n=====<ins>Made in UK:</ins>=====<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\"><a href=\"http://Lovestruck.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FLovestruck.com&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8HwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=061fbbf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Lovestruck.com</a></span>（應該係源自英國，但好似畀香港公司 DateTix 收購咗）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBwa3CY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBwa3CY.jpg&h=f2245f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地鐵、電車都賣過唔少廣告，玩得嘅多數係以結婚為目標，不過要課金，都唔平，以結婚為目標嘛<br />\n<br />\n=====<ins>Made in Singapore:</ins>=====<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">LunchClick</span> (by Lunch Actually)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WSNmpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WSNmpG.jpg&h=4a6ab707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩得嘅多數係以結婚為目標，要玩要身份認證，以約會為主調，不過搞到咁，當然要課金，$45x 港紙一個月，或者 $17x 一個月，但要畀足 12 個月月費<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">eSynchrony</span> (eSync) (by Lunch Actually)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8b6BX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8b6BX4.jpg&h=4a62458d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同樣，玩得嘅多數係以結婚為目標，要玩要身份認證，畢業證書，乜乜證書&hellip;&hellip;要答好多問題，大約個幾星期後會有佢哋篩選過嘅對象畀你。同樣，又係同上一樣，請課金 please<br />\n<br />\n以上兩個 apps 出自同一公司 Lunch Actually 手筆</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b87da87a9e7c7714f5b8081b06f4c4b8693bf152","tid":2201074,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有關 <span class=\"red\">Lunch Click</span>、<span class=\"red\">eSynchrony (eSync)</span> 同埋 <span class=\"red\">Lovestruck</span>，可以睇吓呢個 blog 嘅評測：<br />\n<ins>Lunch Actually / Esynchrony / Lovestruck 三大dating 公司比拼 (三) 價錢篇</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://cranberrydiary.wordpress.com/2017/05/17/lunch-actually-esynchrony-lovestruck-%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7dating-%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%AF%94%E6%8B%BC-%E4%B8%89-%E5%83%B9%E9%8C%A2%E7%AF%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcranberrydiary.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F05%2F17%2Flunch-actually-esynchrony-lovestruck-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7dating-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25AF%2594%25E6%258B%25BC-%25E4%25B8%2589-%25E5%2583%25B9%25E9%258C%25A2%25E7%25AF%2587%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8HwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=d077e69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cranberrydiary.wordpress.com/2017/05/17/lunch-actually-esynchrony-lovestruck-%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7dating-%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%AF%94%E6%8B%BC-%E4%B8%89-%E5%83%B9%E9%8C%A2%E7%AF%87/</a><br />\n摘要：<br />\n「－ <ins>Lunch Actually</ins><br />\n5 Dates / 1 year membership / around $9,000<br />\nUnlimited / 1 year membership / around $16,000<br />\n－ <ins>eSynchrony (eSync)</ins><br />\nAt least 10 Dates / 1 year membership /  $5,700<br />\nAt least 15 Dates / 1.5 year membership /  $6,500<br />\n－ <ins>Lovestruck</ins><br />\n一開始佢sell我有三個packages，一萬頭，一萬中，最貴好似4萬幾」<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">Paktor</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxokGri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfxokGri.jpg&h=85f271b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想溝新加坡仔仔／女女，呢個 app 就啱你，因為好少香港人<br />\n<br />\n=====<ins>Made in Thailand:</ins>=====<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">Noonswoon</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DmRyg0j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDmRyg0j.jpg&h=4d7abd5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同樣以結婚為目標，課金好似要六百幾七百港紙，應該係以年計<br />\n以上個 app 被香港公司 DateTix 收購咗，source:<br />\n－ <ins>促成15對情人，泰國約會應用Noonswoon被香港競爭對手Datetix收購</ins> <a href=\"http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1221355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksilicon.com%2Farticles%2F1221355&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8HwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=b0bd18f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1221355</a><br />\n－ <ins>金風玉露點相逢？DateTix搭橋鋪路吸金</ins> <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20160524/bkn-20160524121949891-0524_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20160524%2Fbkn-20160524121949891-0524_00842_001.html&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8HwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=a997fc04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20160524/bkn-20160524121949891-0524_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n=====<ins>Made in Taiwan:</ins>=====<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">WeTouch</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3FLOQpF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3FLOQpF.jpg&h=a63f6950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對象係大學生，台灣本土當然較多，而香港唔太常用<br />\n屬 &rsquo;freemium app&rsquo;，進階功能先要課金，免費都用得﹐同 Tinder 差唔多（介面都差唔多）<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">iPair</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12Ds5Y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12Ds5Y3.jpg&h=0b8e1bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對象係大學生至中女。都有唔少賓賓，系統有時又會整啲一睇就知係台灣／假嘅 profile picture (bots)，令你覺得有人 match 你 ，繼而叫你課金解鎖解功能  。想傾計就必先盛惠 $17x / month，不過相信唔會有人想畀 $17x 同賓賓交友<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">SweetRing</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4xmqY7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4xmqY7.jpg&h=da71e0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ViHmqY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FViHmqY8.jpg&h=3f6caf37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對象係要結婚嘅人，相對比較少「假人」。但同樣，同想傾計嘅話，請先盛惠 ~$500，一畀要畀 3 個月 ，仲貴過 Tinder 或者其他出名啲嘅交友 apps<br />\n真是荒謬，把自己看得那麼高<br />\n<br />\n而上面呢三個台灣 apps 都係出自同一間公司，source：<br />\n<ins>愛情公寓止跌回升！婚戀交友app「SweetRing」成營收成長主力:</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/39177/BN-2016-04-11-145414-44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Farticle%2F39177%2FBN-2016-04-11-145414-44&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8HwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=0c6a23d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/39177/BN-2016-04-11-145414-44</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVG6B6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVG6B6h.jpg&h=2a91c001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n資料不足，需要各位巴打絲打補完（出自咩國家／地區？玩法？男女質素等等）：<br />\n<br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">BeeTalk</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpSp8dz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpSp8dz.jpg&h=d8ac14f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&gt; <span class=\"red\">SayHi</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6bqSFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6bqSFh.jpg&h=fe4372ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家集思廣益 ，早日揾到你值得擁有既另一半 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6c5349227c3ae1f44b59e81b848c6ed4620c3f06","tid":2201074,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"[Tg] 放低TG就會有人搵? (96)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2174499\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2174499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"365cd23f314194716598c479bd793e8ddbe651a2","tid":2201074,"uid":206008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT